claim: One of the Five Pillars of Islam is the pilgrimage.
premise_source_doc_sentence: Fasting the month of Ramadan is one of the five pillars of Islam , as shown by a quote from the Companion Abdullah ibn Umar ibn al-Khattab : `` I heard the Messenger of Allah  (  Allah bless him and give him peace  )  say : ` The religion of Islam is based upon five  (  pillars  )  : testifying that there is no deity except God and Muhammad is the Messenger of God ; establishing the prayer ; giving zakat ; making pilgrimage ; and fasting  (  the month  )  of Ramadan . ' ''
